title: robeson
description:
A collection of the music of Paul Robeson. 

This compilation includes the well known and the less well known songs of Robeson.

Many of the songs are copied from the old records, so if there are plenty of jumps and crackles just enjoy the music as it was it in years gone by. Don`t forget, this man suffered in his pursuit of equality and recognition. If you want to know more,please google Paul Robeson and learn. sorry I have not listed the songs but there are about 90 of them.  
Happy listening.
